Despite the discomfort my HR was not bad so decided to give myself the best shot at the workout. We’ll see if I do the double threshold. William Cuthbertson Benjamin Allen helped push me to finish the workout and led most of the reps! Splits (3:06, 3:08.3, 3:06.6., 3:10.2, 3:10.0, 3:10.4, 3:11.3, 3:15.8, 3:10.7, 3:13.2, 3:14.2, 3:04.6)

3 by flying 40m, 3 by standing 50m, and 10 100m strides at 12 seconds with one minute rest. Speed went great today, got a lot faster in just 5 weeks! Splits for 100m’s (12.8, 13.2, 12.8, 13.0, 12.5, 12.5, 12.3, 12.5, 12.0, 12.4)
Ran with Rory Linkletter today! Fun to chat with another Puma rep.

Activity Name: 4 by mile with one minute rest! 4:57 average
Altitude hill workout! 6 by 1 minute, 6 by 40 sec, 6 by 20 secs
Description: 5 minute rest in between sets, active recovery back down in between reps. 1 minutes were brutal! Thought I was going to bail out. Thankfully the rest of the workout went well. 1 minutes were mile pace, 40 secs were 800 pace, 20 secs were sprints!

Activity Name: Ran only 11.5 today! 😓 Ran into a gust of wind and it was cold 🥶 will get sub 11 next week though 💪

Description: Feeling pretty good! Got a massage this morning at it helped a lot!

Unfortunately didn’t have a chance to run sub 11. But Coach promise me I’ll do it this indoor season! So sun 11 around the corner!

Activity Name: Best tempo of my life! Had my friends help pace me with bikes! Altitude works!
